{"tid":1503371,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"入機場者等同割蓆葵青人","createTime":"2019-08-25T03:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T06:15:47.000Z","uid":290594,"like":16,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4a961003bfe2e742f003adedc361f81c0a9e86a4","tid":1503371,"uid":290594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:16:12.000Z","msg":"我地葵青人已經忍左一次<br />\n上訴成功左<br />\n家下你同我講入機場<br />\n咁同割蓆有咩分<br />\n其實真心好好玩？<br />\n文宣用左一個星期<br />\n你用一個鐘就拉人走入機場<br />\n不如咁，自己去搞以後<br />\n次撚次都漠視葵青人，同林㭍有乜分別<br />\n入機場不如做冷氣軍師啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">總之一句，葵涌運動場等</span></strong></span><br />\n有手足咁仲入機場，醒下啦<br />\n驚就唔好出街啦<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mt0u0er.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmt0u0er.jpg&h=1ffa4533&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"172fc9e8579a779bc49d67dc14d3813c4d7b4f03","tid":1503371,"uid":110509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,未必CALL 到人, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後既每個星期六/日 要起碼有一日一定係機場，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜撚都要讓路!!</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"0ba17c5e50ccebc103689fee01e1b6f4b165b8a5","tid":1503371,"uid":110509,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:17:14.000Z","msg":"#290594<br />\n分化撚"},{"pid":"be19fc79d9932f44fe45e826b9dcc2380df50899","tid":1503371,"uid":35699,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:17:30.000Z","msg":"之後入得唔得呀<br />\nbe water 嗰陣唔去九龍去機場得唔得呀"},{"pid":"a25c0ab52bda939e1fd05e8ba2db4a1fd331f668","tid":1503371,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:17:37.000Z","msg":"見到今日機